//     - Defined store_entry struct for packed struct (address, data, be, data_size, cbo_op, valid, wait_rvalid)
//     - Converted speculative_queue and commit_queue to reg arrays using store_entry struct
//     - Rewrote always_comb core_if with proper Anvil let bindings and conditionals
//     - Rewrote always_comb store_if with proper FSM logic for commit queue drain
//     - Rewrote always_comb address_checker with for loops over both queues
//     - Rewrote always_ff blocks as loop with set := syntax
//     - Fixed increment/decrement of status counters (no ++ / -- in Anvil)
//     - Fixed pointer arithmetic for circular buffer management
//   MANUAL-CLEANUP-NEEDED items:
//     - Parameter handling (CVA6Cfg, DEPTH_SPEC, DEPTH_COMMIT) needs Anvil param support
